' last_updated: 2026-05-30
@startuml runtime-logging-flow

title runtime-logging — console 接管 + 落盘 sequence (init / main 直写 / renderer IPC bridge / fatal)

participant "renderer 业务\n(console.* / log.scope)" as RBiz
participant "renderer logger\n(electron-log/renderer)" as RLog
participant "main 业务\n(console.* / log.scope)" as MBiz
participant "main logger\n(electron-log/main)" as MLog
participant "file transport" as FT
database "main-YYYY-MM-DD.log" as File

== 启动 init (main logger.ts 顶层 import 即跑) ==

MLog -> MLog: app.setName('Agent Deck') (必先于 app.getPath('logs'))
MLog -> MLog: log.initialize() (装 IPC bridge: preload 注入 + __electronLog.sendToMain)
MLog -> FT: resolvePathFn = main-<today>.log + cleanupOldLogs(14 天)
MLog -> FT: file.level='info' / console.level='silly'
MLog -> MLog: errorHandler.startCatching({ showDialog: !isPackaged })
note right of MLog
  console 接管 Object.assign(console, log.functions) (NODE_ENV=test 跳过)
  bootstrap 后按持久化 logLevel 补 setFileLevel (启动即生效)
end note

== main 进程日志直写 ==

MBiz -> MLog: logger.info('...') / 被接管的 console.log
MLog -> FT: 格式化 [time] [level] (scope) msg
FT -> File: 同步写

== renderer 日志经 IPC bridge 落同一份 ==

RBiz -> RLog: logger.info('...') / 被接管的 console.log
RLog -> MLog: electron-log 内部 IPC (__electronLog.sendToMain)
MLog -> FT: 同一 file transport
FT -> File: 落同一份 main-<today>.log

== fatal: uncaughtException 落盘 + 强退 ==

MBiz -> MLog: uncaughtException 抛出
MLog -> FT: errorHandler 落盘 (electron-log file 同步写在前)
FT -> File: 写 fatal stack
MLog -> MBiz: app.exit(1)
note right of MLog
  本 uncaughtException listener 在 electron-log listener 之后注册
  → Node 按注册序调 → 先落盘后退出 (恢复 Node 默认 fatal 语义)
  unhandledRejection 仅落盘不强退 (避免单个 stray rejection 杀进程)
end note

== preload fatal (contextBridge 失败 / preload 加载失败) ==

RBiz -> MLog: PreloadFatalError IPC (fire-and-forget) / webContents preload-error
MLog -> FT: preload-fatal scope error 落盘
FT -> File: 写

@enduml
